sql:
SELECT participant_name
FROM participants
WHERE age < (SELECT AVG(age) FROM participants);

external_knowledge:
- "blossoms" metaphorically represents individual trial instances;
- "gardens" metaphorically represents researchers;
- "sown more than two seeds" refers to having conducted more than two experimental sessions;
- "beyond the average" indicates a trial duration that exceeds the average duration for trials conducted by the same researcher.

